Welcome:

   The Directorate for Education and Human Resources (EHR) is responsible
   for the health and continued vitality of the Nation's science,
   mathematics, engineering, and technology education and for providing
   leadership in the effort to improve education in these areas.

Headlines:

     * The National Science Board has approved the Math and Science
       Partnership (MSP) Program, part of the President's Initiative, No
       Child Left Behind, to strengthen and reform pre K-12 education. .

